stories.title: It's now Carisbrook or bust for England and New Zealand
stories.summary: New Zealand gave it a go, but without a steady top order contribution it was always going to struggle to score the 223 needed to beat England and prevent the National Bank Series being tied up 2-2 going in Tuesday's last match
